connectReply:
  • Status: ok, ko, move, destroyed
  • [new AAL space coordinator EP]

The node coordinator:
  • create a new AAL Space
  • Join to an existing AAL Space
  • Federates to an existing AAL Space

This operation allows the node to alert the coordinator that about his presence. The node can look for services, provide services. The connect can fail in case of:
  • the securityToken is no more valid. In this case the node can invoke the join operation
  • AAL Space Coordinator is no more available and the operation fails
  • AAL Space Coordinator is still present but without the role of coordinator
